SELECT c.name, d.income, pref.category, r.report_type FROM customers c JOIN demographics d ON c.customer_id = d.customer_id JOIN preferences pref ON c.customer_id = pref.customer_id JOIN reports r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id WHERE d.income > 70000.00 AND pref.preference_score > 7;

SELECT c.name, d.occupation, r.report_type, r.generated_date FROM customers c JOIN demographics d ON c.customer_id = d.customer_id JOIN reports r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id WHERE d.income > 80000.00 AND r.report_type = 'Annual';

SELECT DISTINCT c.name, d.education_level, p.product_name, r.report_type FROM customers c JOIN demographics d ON c.customer_id = d.customer_id JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id JOIN reports r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id WHERE d.income > 90000.00 AND p.quantity > 2;

SELECT c.name, d.income, p.product_name, r.report_type FROM customers c JOIN demographics d ON c.customer_id = d.customer_id JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id JOIN reports r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id WHERE d.occupation = 'Engineer';

SELECT c.name, d.occupation, p.product_name, pref.category, r.report_type FROM customers c JOIN demographics d ON c.customer_id = d.customer_id JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id JOIN preferences pref ON c.customer_id = pref.customer_id JOIN reports r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id WHERE r.report_type = 'Bi-Weekly' AND pref.preference_score > 8;

SELECT c.name, d.education_level, p.product_name, p.quantity, p.price, r.report_type FROM customers c JOIN demographics d ON c.customer_id = d.customer_id JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id JOIN reports r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id WHERE d.occupation = 'Doctor' AND p.price > 200.00;

SELECT c.name, d.income, p.product_name, p.quantity, r.report_type, r.generated_date FROM customers c JOIN demographics d ON c.customer_id = d.customer_id JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id JOIN reports r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id WHERE d.education_level = 'Masters' AND r.report_type = 'Weekly';

SELECT c.name, d.occupation, p.product_name, p.price, pref.category, r.report_type, r.generated_date FROM customers c JOIN demographics d ON c.customer_id = d.customer_id JOIN purchases p ON c.customer_id = p.customer_id JOIN preferences pref ON c.customer_id = pref.customer_id JOIN reports r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id WHERE pref.preference_score > 9 AND r.report_type = 'Bi-Annual' AND d.income > 100000.00;
